summary: .bat file for launching \"Realistic Lighting Patcher.jar\" if you have .jar files associated with a non-java program.
descriptionHtml:
.bat file for launching \"Realistic Lighting Patcher.jar\" if you have .jar files associated with a non-java program and don\'t know how to re-associate it with java (or are to lazy to do so, such as myself).

It assumes that \'java\' is correctly assigned in your PATH.
Which it should be.
If you have java installed.
Correctly.

I may make more that DON\'T assume that java is properly installed if there is a need for it.
